The paper discusses security risk assessment methods in the context of IoT systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The research also involves consulting with industry professionals to understand wider concerns and key challenges, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR), software engineering (cs.SE), cyber security (cs.CY), and systems and control (cs.SI).
